ygData.subject: RE: [EverQuest] Server GM email adress
ygData.msgSnippet: All guides KNOW the server lead gm adress. its part of their job. If you cant get the info then ask for the serverwide swat GM, there is always a serverwide GM
ygData.messageBody:
All guides KNOW the server lead gm adress. its part of their job. If you
cant get the info then ask for the serverwide swat GM, there is always a
serverwide GM online, often quite busy though. I cant help you with Tunares
lead GM adress , but this is how it works.



-----Original Message-----
From: Nygaard, Jeff [mailto:jeff.nygaard@...]
Sent: Monday, May 20, 2002 7:32 PM
To: EverQuest@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [EverQuest] Server GM email adress


Does anyone know a web site where I can get the email address of my servers
Lead GM? I have a problem, the guide that helped was great a gave us as much
information as she could and said she would pass it along to the GM. She
instructed me to do a petition on Sunday through Thursday from 3 pm to 6 pm
Pacific time. I did this yesterday and no real GM ever showed up and the
guide that answered me yesterday was a guide and said I would have to keep
trying. I would like to get his email address to start a dialog about the
problem I have.

Anyone know the web site or the Tunare Lead GM email address?
